Step 2: Clone the new GitHub repository to your computer via RStudio

  • In RStudio, start a new Project:
    • File > New Project > Version Control > Git repository URL GitHub repository URL . ex) https://github.com/bensoltoff/myrepo.git
  • Open in new session
  • Creat Project ( Git ) .
